<h1> MyTranslator</h1>
<h2> MyTranslator</h2>
<p>
MyTranslator ,
, /, .
,
API.
</p>
<p>
:
<ul>
<li><code>LanguageDetectionComponent</code>
API (, langdetect,
Google Language Detection API).</li>
<li><code>TextTranslationSubsystem</code>
API (Google
Translate, DeepL, Yandex.Translate).</li>
<li><code>IOTextModule</code> ,
TXT, DOCX PDF.</li>
<li><code>VoiceInputOutputMechanism</code> ,
API Google Speech-to-
Text, Microsoft Azure Speech .</li>
<li><code>UserInterface</code> ,
.</li>
<li><code>TranslationHistorySystem</code> ,
, .</li>
<li><code>BrowserIntegrationModule</code>
, .</li>
<li><code>CustomSettingsModule</code> ,
, .</li>
<li><code>DataSecurityBlock</code> ,
.</li>
</ul>
</p>
<h2> </h2>
<h3> 1: </h3>
<p>
<code>LanguageDetectionComponent</code>
.
</p>
<pre><code>
# LanguageDetectionComponent
lang_detector = LanguageDetectionComponent()
#
text = "Bonjour, comment a va?"
detected_language = lang_detector.run(text)
</code></pre>
<p>
.
</p>
<h3> 2: </h3>
<p>
<code>TextTranslationSubsystem</code>
.
</p>
<pre><code>
# TextTranslationSubsystem
translator = TextTranslationSubsystem()
#
original_text = "Bonjour, comment a va?"
translated_text = translator.run(original_text, source_lang="fr", target_lang="ru")
</code></pre>
<p>
.
</p>
<h3> 3: </h3>
<p>
<code>IOTextModule</code>
.
</p>
<pre><code>
# IOTextModule
io_module = IOTextModule()
#
user_input = "Hello, how are you?"
io_module.input_text(user_input)
#
translated = translator.run(user_input, source_lang="en", target_lang="ru")
io_module.output_text(translated)
</code></pre>
<p>
,
.
</p>
<h3> 4: </h3>
<p>
<code>VoiceInputOutputMechanism</code>
.
</p>
<pre><code>
# VoiceInputOutputMechanism
voice_module = VoiceInputOutputMechanism()
#
voice_input = voice_module.capture()
translated_voice = translator.run(voice_input, source_lang="en", target_lang="ru")
voice_module.speak(translated_voice)
</code></pre>
<p>
. </p>
<h3> 5: </h3>
<p>
<code>TranslationHistorySystem</code>
.
</p>
<pre><code>
# TranslationHistorySystem
history_system = TranslationHistorySystem()
#
history_system.save(original_text, translated_text)
#
result = history_system.search(query="Bonjour")
</code></pre>
<p>
,
.
</p>
<h3> 6: </h3>
<p>
<code>BrowserIntegrationModule</code>
.
</p>
<pre><code>
# BrowserIntegrationModule
browser_module = BrowserIntegrationModule()
#
translated_text = browser_module.run("Hello, world!")
</code></pre>
<p>
.
</p>
<h3> 7: </h3>
<p>
<code>CustomSettingsModule</code>
.
</p>
<pre><code>
# CustomSettingsModule
settings_module = CustomSettingsModule()
# (, )
settings_module.set_preferences(source_lang="en", target_lang="ru", theme="dark")
</code></pre>
<p>
.
</p>
<h3> 8: </h3>
<p>
<code>DataSecurityBlock</code>
.
</p>
<pre><code>
# DataSecurityBlock
security_block = DataSecurityBlock()
#
encrypted_data = security_block.encrypt(translated_text)
</code></pre>
<p>
,
.
